{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"65b755f46f","title":"大字报诗——长恨歌","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（一）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编，1957年8月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d6f929222d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"65b755f46f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"e18e852377","name":"山西师范学院学生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6d72d635f5","type":"title","text":"大字报诗——长恨歌","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"65b755f46f"},{"id":"36ccfe8309","type":"authors","text":"山西师范学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"65b755f46f"},{"id":"99580cc3a3","type":"paragraph","text":"师院最重公共课，千呼万唤改不得；我本物理专修科，专修几门公共课；","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"65b755f46f"},{"id":"a9474c8295","type":"paragraph","text":"每周上课32节， 国际水平早突破；公共课程内容繁，上天下地都学遍；","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"65b755f46f"},{"id":"9b28f76ffe","type":"paragraph","text":"划蛇添足狗续貂，叠林架屋洪水泛；条条类类满黑板，大本小本笔记满；","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"65b755f46f"},{"id":"710688e311","type":"paragraph","text":"笔记虽多尽教条，放之四海而皆惨；专业学习大相反，大刀阔斧一起喊；","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"65b755f46f"},{"id":"0fa4c02184","type":"paragraph","text":"教学课程商量明，简而不明是特点；物理课本虽然好，先生的课会精简；","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"65b755f46f"},{"id":"68f7109a81","type":"paragraph","text":"剪头去尾长变短，七折八扣拦腰斩；闻到数学据大纲，大纲决定在中央；","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"65b755f46f"},{"id":"bdcecc63bc","type":"paragraph","text":"退之万里高教部，不见长安只见雾；今年混过复明年，秋月春风等闲渡；","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"65b755f46f"},{"id":"7660dba060","type":"paragraph","text":"腹中冷落知识稀，老大把人子弟误；如此师院太可怜，人类灵魂工程师；","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"65b755f46f"},{"id":"fd64572f93","type":"paragraph","text":"领导充耳全不闻，学生意见齐禁止；同是中国读书人，相逢何如都害死；","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"65b755f46f"},{"id":"159a04d87e","type":"paragraph","text":"读罢落泪我最多，并州司羔不想吃。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"65b755f46f"},{"id":"8081ad5243","type":"paragraph","text":"——白居难——","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"65b755f46f"}],"page":{"id":"1ee93b17a6","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"65b755f46f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}